  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Left and Right Inverses",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $f : A \\to B$.\n\nA \\emph{left inverse} of $f$ is a function $g : B \\to A$ with $g \\circ f = \\id_A$.\n\nA \\emph{right inverse} (or \\emph{section}) of $f$ is a function $h : B \\to A$\nwith $f \\circ h = \\id_B$.",
